<h1>X1 Algebra </h1>

This is the course home page for X1 Algebra 
as provided by the Centre for Mathematical Science 
for 1st year Students.
<p>

The syllabus for this course can be found
<a href="http://www.city.ac.uk/mathematics/Syllabus/Year1.html">
here</a>. 

Unless otherwise stated, all files for download are in .pdf format.

<!-- }}} -->
