<p> Mar 2004: EXAM REVISION - 
There are now links below to the 2003 exam paper, and to
model solutions to that paper. It is recommended that you do not look 
at the solutions until after you have attempted the paper as a mock exam 
under exam conditions.
There will be revision lectures in week 1 of summer term - be sure to have
attempted the mock exam before this, and bring any questions you have
along to the lectures for discussion.
<p> April 2004: EXAM REVISION - 
There are now links below to the 2003 RESIT exam paper, and to
model solutions to that paper. This will serve well as another  
mock exam for this year.

